0zero.%20A%20year%20before%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraveling-first-trimester-pregnancy-tips-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efirst%20pregnancy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20launched%20a%20fashion%20blog%20as%20a%20creative%20outlet.%20In%20the%20early%202010s%2C%20it%20was%20the%20golden%20age%20of%20blogging.%20Readers%20loved%20personal%20stories%20mixed%20with%20outfit%20inspiration%2C%20and%20brands%20were%20eager%20to%20collaborate%20with%20bloggers%20who%20had%20even%20a%20modest%20following.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20announced%20my%20first%20pregnancy%20on%20the%20blog%2C%20I%20noticed%20more%20traffic%20and%20comments%20than%20ever%20before.%20Readers%20wanted%20to%20know%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-maternity-clothing%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ematernity%20clothes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20baby%20gear%2C%20and%20how%20I%20was%20juggling%20it%20all.%20Then%2C%20just%20three%20months%20after%20my%20son's%20birth%2C%20I%20shared%20the%20news%20of%20my%20second%20pregnancy.%20That's%20when%20things%20truly%20snowballed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPartnership%20offers%20flooded%20my%20inbox.%20Suddenly%2C%20I%20wasn't%20just%20writing%20for%20fun%3B%20I%20was%20becoming%20a%20partner%20to%20companies%20that%20wanted%20to%20reach%20young%20mothers%20like%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e787d8d0-0ce8-43cf-8461-d8fca42a3b9e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20children%20grew%20up%20with%20opportunities%20I%20never%20expected%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20early%20partnerships%20changed%20everything.%20I%20never%20bought%20a%20stroller%2C%20a%20car%20seat%2C%20or%20even%20most%20of%20my%20children's%20clothes.%20They%20arrived%20at%20my%20door%20through%20collaborations%20with%20brands%20eager%20to%20feature%20their%20products%20on%20my%20blog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20went%20far%20beyond%20the%20essentials.%20Thanks%20to%20blogging%20and%20later%20my%20Instagram%20presence%2C%