%20height%3D%5C%22989%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20built%20her%20itny%20house%20with%20help.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Louise%20Southerden%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20enlisted%20a%20few%20helpers%2C%20the%20main%20one%20being%20my%20partner%20at%20the%20time%2C%20Max.%20A%20retired%20scientist%20and%20a%20talented%20woodworker%2C%20Max%20had%20all%20the%20tools%20we%20would%20need%20and%2C%20importantly%2C%20a%20place%20where%20we%20could%20do%20the%20build%3A%20the%20driveway%20beside%20his%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20September%202020%2C%20we'd%20started%20work%20on%20the%20floor%20and%20the%20timber%20frame.%20Then%20came%20the%20windows%2C%20the%20cladding%2C%20and%20the%20roof.%20Max's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fage-gap-best-friend-friendship-lessons-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20friend%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20retired%20builder%2C%20helped%20out%20for%20the%20first%20couple%20of%20months%20to%20ensure%20everything%20was%20structurally%20sound.%20After%20that%2C%20Max%20and%20I%20worked%20six%2C%20often%20seven%2C%20days%20a%20week%20on%20the%20interior%20fit-out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20all%20intensely%20fascinating%2C%20exhausting%2C%20and%20stressful%2C%20because%20as%20my%20tiny%20house%20was%20coming%20together%2C%20our%20relationship%20began%20falling%20apart.%20It%20didn't%20survive%20the%20build%2C%20but%20we%20managed%20to%20keep%20working%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAfter%20eight%20months%2C%20my%20beautiful%20little%20house%20was%20done.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20author's%20tiny%20house%20inside%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e69c225dbc4fd10daa742b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EInside%20the%20author's%20tiny%20house.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Rasa%20Pescud%3A%20Living%20Big%20in%20a%20Tiny%20House%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ff