w%20call%20romantasy%2C%20many%20of%20those%20books%20were%20shelved%20young%20adult.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20characters%20in%20%26quot%3BDaughter%20of%20No%20Worlds%26quot%3B%20are%20in%20their%2020s%2C%20not%20their%20teens.%20Broadbent%20%E2%80%94%20who%20said%20she%20%26quot%3Bwas%20also%20terrified%20of%20querying%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20didn't%20want%20her%20book%20to%20get%20picked%20up%20if%20it%20meant%20she%20had%20to%20age%20down%20her%20characters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20believed%20that%20if%20I%20had%20tried%20to%20query%20this%2C%20that%20traditional%20publishing%20would%20have%20wanted%20me%20to%20make%20all%20of%20the%20characters%20three%20years%20younger%20and%20put%20it%20in%20upper%20young%20adult%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20felt%20really%20strongly%20that%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20do%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20she%20self-published%20the%20novel%2C%20Broadbent%20ensured%20%26quot%3BDaughter%20of%20No%20Worlds%26quot%3B%20stayed%20true%20to%20her%20vision.%20By%20the%20time%20Bramble%20picked%20up%20the%20%26quot%3BCrowns%20of%20Nyaxia%26quot%3B%20series%2C%20both%20Broadbent%20and%20romantasy%20were%20established%20enough%20that%20she%20could%20continue%20writing%20romantic%20fantasy%20with%20adult%20characters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fself-publishing-benefits-romantasy-author-carissa-broadbent-interview-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1760180881000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e7ff52cc993f9955cfe6a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fself-publishing-benefits-romantasy-author-carissa-broadbent-interview-2025-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bestselling%20romantasy%20author%20Carissa%20Broadbent%20says%20self-publishing%20can%20be%20more%20lucrative%20than%20traditional%20publishing%20and