20NextGen%20Acela%20had%20retractable%20window%20shades%2C%20which%20made%20the%20car%20look%20less%20cluttered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20train%20also%20added%20screens%20with%20information%20about%20the%20ride%20on%20the%20walls%20and%20ceilings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20older%20car%20had%20large%20seats%2C%20but%20I%20thought%20they%20felt%20stiff.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20aerial%20view%20of%20the%20author%20sitting%20in%20her%20business-class%20seat%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68ac6f49194a2d49b8af18b9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20business-class%20seat%20on%20the%20first%20Acela%20was%2020%20inches%20wide%20and%2026%20feet%20deep.%20There%20was%20a%20tray%20table%2C%20a%20reading%20light%20overhead%2C%20and%20two%20power%20outlets%20on%20the%20wall%20beneath%20the%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20had%20a%20footrest%2C%20the%20option%20to%20recline%2C%20and%20plenty%20of%20legroom%2C%20thanks%20to%20a%2042-inch%20seat%20pitch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20seats%20on%20the%20NextGen%20Acela%20were%20sleeker%20and%20more%20comfortable.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20a%20business-class%20seat%20on%20an%20Amtrak%20Next%20Gen%20Acela%20train%20and%20the%20seatback%20with%20a%20cupholder%20on%20it%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68d44344183847aa39d766eb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chairs%20on%20my%20second%20ride%20were%20noticeably%20thinner%2C%20but%20I%20found%20them%20to%20be%20much%20more%20comfortable.%20The%20cushions%20felt%20softer%2C%20and%20the%20material%20felt%20smoother.%20The%20ne