0looking%20at%20it%20over%20a%20longer%20window.%20That's%20how%20I%20make%20sure%20I%20still%20spend%20quality%20time%20with%20my%20family.%20Before%2C%20I%20could%20look%20at%20a%2024-hour%20day%20and%20decide%20how%20many%20hours%20I%20would%20spend%20on%20exercising%20or%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20just%20can't%20do%20that%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d6dfc2a6-5016-4262-8347-04556781800f%5C%22%3EBreast-pumping%20provides%20some%20daily%20structure%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20smartwatch%20wakes%20me%20up%20at%206%20a.m.%20I%20start%20the%20day%20really%20quickly%20by%20checking%20on%20Slack%20and%20email.%20We%20run%20a%2024%2F7%20business%2C%20and%20hospitals%20need%20to%20check%20if%20anything%20has%20come%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20get%20up%20at%20six%20so%20that%20I%20can%20quickly%20get%20set%20up%20as%20a%20mother%20of%20a%2010-month-old%2C%20still%20breastfeeding%2C%20and%20do%20my%20first%20pump%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20annoying%20thing%20about%20breastfeeding%20is%20that%20I'm%20trying%20my%20best%20to%20watch%20my%20caffeine%20intake.%20I%20make%20a%20weird%20half-coffee%2C%20half-decaf%2C%20half-regular%20mix%20every%20morning%2C%20so%20at%20least%20I%20get%20some%20caffeine.%20No%20way%20I'm%20getting%20through%20the%20day%20without%20it%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20diluted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20aim%20for%20every%20three%20to%20four%20hours%20between%20each%20pump%2C%20or%20else%20I%20start%20to%20worry%20about%20having%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fhow-to-increase-milk-supply%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emy%20supply%20drop%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20not%20having%20enough%20milk%20for%20my%20little%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20created%20an%20interesting%20structure%20where%20I%20can%20schedule%20meetings%2C%20have%20meals%2C%20and%20so%20on%2C%20within%20these%20blocks%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I'm%20pumping%2C%20I%20usually%20use%20that%20time%20at%20my%20desk%2C%20going%20through%20emails%20and%20working%20on%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20really%20random%20thing%20that%20I've%20picked%20up%2C%20because%20breastfeeding%20just%20takes%20so%20much%20energy%2C%20is%20that%20every%20night%20around%209%20p.m.%20I'm%20eating%20a%20late-night%20snack%2C%20which%20I've%20never%20done%20before.%20I%20try%20to%20do%20a%20plain%20Greek%20yogurt%20with%20fruit%20and%20a%20pack%20of%20peanuts%20mixed%20in.%20Something%20that's%20high%20protein%20and%20relatively%20low%20sugar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%209%3A30%20p.m.%2C%20I%20hop%20back%20onto%20my%20work%20computer%20to%20check%20on%20any%20last-minute%20or%20crucial%20items%20that%20have%20come%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20use%20this%20time%20to%20plan%20out%20critical%20tasks%20for%20the%20next%20day%2C%20make%20sure%20that%20my%20pump%20sessions%20that%20I've%20outlined%2C%20I%20have%20those%20blocks%20because%20meetings%20come%20in%20and%20out%2C%20and%20I%20have%20to%20shift%20them%20sometimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20I%20do%20one%20final%20pump%20again%20at%2010%3A30%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b781d088-ba61-440d-99e4-8614f6bd8ee6%5C%22%3EOne%20'stupid%20gripe'%20that%20says%20a%20lot%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20a%20very%20different%20experience%20being%20the%20birth%20parent.%20I%20had%20a%20routine%20with%20our%20first%20child%2C%20but%20this%20is%20new.%20It's%20shown%20me%20how%20we%20still%20need%20to%20have%20more%20conversations%20around%20navigating%20motherhood%2C%20including%20logistics%20like%20how%20to%20prep%20for%20a%20business%20travel%2C%20what%20equipment%20you%20need%20to%20bring%2C%20or%20how%20the%20first%20trimester%20can%20be%20%3Cem%3Ereally%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20actually%20a%20stupid%20gripe%20that%20I've%20had%2C%20and%20it's%20how%20I've%20gone%20to%20many%20conferences%20where%20I've%20had%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20pump%2C%20and%20I'm%20flabbergasted%20at%20how%20few%20have%20thought%20about%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20at%20one%20conference%20with%202%2C000%20attendees%2C%20and%20not%20one%20had%20a%20mother's%20room.%20I%20had%20to%20go%20into%20the%20bathroom%20and%20stand%20there%20for%2020%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20only%20one%20conference%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Bezos%20Mars%20Conference%20%E2%80%94%20that%20did%20such%20an%20amazing%20job%2C%20where%20they%20had%20a%20separate%20mother's%20room%2C%20and%20it%20would%20livestream%20the%20event.%20You%20didn't%20miss%20out%20on%20key%20sessions%2C%20so%20they%20were%20super%20thoughtful%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20also%20discovered%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbreastfeeding-rooms-required-major-us-airports-law-2018-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eairport%20mothers'%20rooms%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20fantastic%2C%20and%20I'm%20very%20glad%20that%20those%20are%20actually%20in%20good%20shape.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20I%20think%20we%20should%20be%20having%20more%20of%20this%20conversation%20%E2%80%94%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20parents%20and%20the%20services%20we%20need%20to%20provide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2247346323-da7b-4868-83bb-064e4e6f8240%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20really%20does%20take%20a%20village%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20a%20support%20system%20is%20crucial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20two%20part-time%20nannies%2C%20not%20because%20we%20need%20both%20of%20them%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20but%20because%20if%20one%20gets%20sick%2C%20we%20won't%20end%20up%20with%20no%20nannies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20also%20amazingly%20lucky%20that%20my%20parents%20and%20the%20kids'%20grandparents%20are%20very%20involved.%20They%20will%20come%20and%20stay%20with%20us%20for%20months%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20there%20are%20days%20when%20there%20will%20be%20no%20one%20left%20to%20call%2C%20and%20you%20have%20to%20prioritize.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20talkin