erfilling%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-furniture-not-good-quality-red-flags-interior-designer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20house%20with%20furniture%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Zinnecker%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20want%20to%20make%20the%20spaces%20feel%20large%2C%20and%20you%20also%20want%20people%20to%20feel%20inspired%20and%20creative%2C%20and%20visualize%20their%20own%20lives%20happening%20in%20the%20house.%20Editing%20and%20paring%20down%20is%20really%20smart.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E4.%20Ignoring%20the%20little%20details%20can%20cost%20you.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228002%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Workers%20cleaning%20a%20home.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e54d7dcc993f9955cfb305%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225337%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWorkers%20cleaning%20a%20home.%3Cp%3ESouth_agency%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EZinnecker%20said%20not%20to%20overlook%20small%20fixes%2C%20like%20baseboard%20repairs%2C%20addressing%20scuffs%20and%20scratches%2C%20and%20touch-up%20paint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20behoove%20sellers%20to%20spend%20a%20little%20on%20those%20items%20to%20make%20the%20home%20feel%20fresh%20and%20new%2C%20and%20less%20lived-in%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20recommends%20hiring%20professional%20cleaners%20and%20investing%20in%20small%20updates%2C%20such%20as%20fresh%20pillows%20and%20kitchen%20decor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnything%20to%20make%20the%20home%20feel%20almost%20like%20a%20boutique%20hotel%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20easy%20way%20to%20make%20it%20feel%20more%20upscale%20than%20it%20might%20actually%20be.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E5.%20Harsh%20artificial%20light%20in%20listing%20photos%20can%20make%20a%20home%20look%20less%20inviting.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20hovering%2