22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStarship%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreated%20by%20Skype%20cofounders%20Ahti%20Heinla%20and%20Janus%20Friis%20in%202014%2C%20Starship%20is%20the%20biggest%20campus%20provider%2C%20providing%20robot%20fleets%20to%2060%20universities.%20The%20company%20said%20it%20has%20over%202%2C000%20robots%20deployed%20on%20campuses%2C%20delivering%20to%201.5%20million%20students.%20It's%20raised%20%24230%20million%2C%20and%20was%20valued%20at%20%24151%20million%20in%20its%20Series%20C%20round%20in%202024%2C%20according%20to%20PitchBook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarship%20said%20it's%20turned%20a%20profit%20on%20each%20delivery%20for%20over%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20optimized%20costs%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20Heinla%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20bettering%20the%20technology%20means%20less%20money%20spent%20on%20repairs%20and%20maintenance.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20now%20at%20the%20point%20where%20the%20unit%20economics%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20UCLA%20Starship%20fleet%20is%20pictured.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e6d37d5dbc4fd10daa7c37%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStarship's%20UCLA%20fleet%20of%20delivery%20robots%3Cp%3EDon%20Liebig%2FDon%20Liebig%2FASUCLA%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EStarship%20has%20partnered%20with%20food%20delivery%20app%20Grubhub%20to%20grow.%20About%20half%20of%20the%20campuses%20Starship%20works%20with%20use%20its%20app%2C%20while%20the%20other%20half%20place%20orders%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethrough%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrubhub-hires-cargill-devry-boughner-vorwer-chief-corporate-affairs-officer-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGrubhub%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Starship%20isn't%20Grubhub's%20only%20partner%3B%20the%20food%20service%20app%20also%20works%20with%20Starship's%20biggest%20direct%20competitor%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FRobot.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERobot.com%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20rapidly%20growing%20Avride.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%2040%20of%20Grubhub's%20campus%20partnerships%20now%20include%20robots.%20Steve%20Iarocci%2C%20senior%20director%20for%20Grubhub%20Campus%2C%20said%20some%20robots%20are%20better%20for%20city%20streets%2C%20and%20others%20are%20better%20for%20pedestrian-only%20campuses.%20%26quot%3BBut%2C%20in%20general%2C%20it's%20pretty%20ubiquitous%20technology%20at%20this%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20singular%20business%20model%20here.%20Contracts%20are%20signed%20between%20the%20robot%20companies%20and%20the%20food%20providers%2C%20though%20Grubhub%20sometimes%20functions%20as%20an%20intermediary.%20Some%20campuses%20pay%20monthly%20costs%20that%20are%20incorporated%20into%20students'%20dining%20plans%3B%20others%20charge%20students%20a%20per-order%20delivery%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bb33014c-04ac-41a8-9b62-2248aa90715c%5C%22%3ERobot.com%20and%20Avride%20race%20behind%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Starship%20is%20leading%20by%20its%20campus%20footprint%2C%20Robot.com%20is%20racing%20behind%20it.%20The%20company%20%E2%80%94%20formerly%20Kiwibot%2C%20as%20its%20robots%20are%20named%20%E2%80%94%20was%20founded%20in%202017%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkiwi-robot-caught-fire-at-uc-berkeley-and-students-were-devastated-2018-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUC%20Berkeley%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20is%20now%20active%20on%2016%20campuses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECofounder%20and%20CEO%20Felipe%20Chavez%20said%20that%20the%20college%20campus%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bour%20sandbox.%26quot%3B%20The%20company%20is%20also%20expanding%20into%20major%20cities%20and%20golf%20courses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobot.com%20raised%20an%20estimated%20%2433%20million%2C%20according%20to%20PitchBook%2C%20though%20the%20company%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20that%20figure%20and%20said%20it's%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20fundraising%20round.%20It%20also%20said%20its%20unit%20economics%20are%20positive%2C%20with%20an%20average%20gross%20margin%20of%2040%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227203%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Kiwibot%20deployment%20at%20Curry%20College%20is%20pictured.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e6d40dcc993f9955cfd544%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224804%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERobot.com's%20Curry%20College%20fleet%20of%20Kiwibots.%3Cp%3ERobot.com%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERobot.com%20recently%20acquired%20an%20ad%20company%20and%20introduced%20robotic%20advertisements.%20Advertising%20makes%20up%2035%25%20to%2040%25%20of%20its%20revenue%2C%20Chavez%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBehind%20Robot.com%20is%20Avride%2C%20a%20US-based%20startup%20spun%20out%20of%20the%20Russian%20company%20Yandex%2C%20which%20faced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyandex-putin-war-ukraine-killed-russia-most-successful-tech-company-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einternational%20sanctions%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20Russia%20invaded%20Ukraine.%20The%20publicly%20traded%20Nebius%20Group%2C%20Avride's%20Dutch%20parent%20company%2C%20sold%20off%20Yandex's%20Russia-based%20assets%20in%202024%20while%20keeping%20some%20of%20its%20AI-focused%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20mainly%20operates%20on%20two%20college%20campuses%2C%20Ohio%20State%20University%20and%20the%20University%20of%20Arizona%2C%20where%20it%20has%20deployed%20165%20robots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChris%20Krnich%2C%20Avride's%20business%20development%20manager%2C%20said%20that%20food%20providers%20saw%20the%20value%20in%20the%20robots%20when%20they%20began%20bringing%20in%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarship%2C%20Robot.com%2C%20and%20Avride%20have%20minor%20differences%20in%20tech.%20Starship%20said%20its%20robots%20are%20the%20most%20adaptive%20to%20different%20environments%3B%20Avride%20also%20makes%20robotaxis%2C%20and%20said%20that%20it%20shrunk%20the%20self-driving%20technology%20into%20their%20delivery%20bots.%20Much%20is%20the%20same%2C%20though.%20They%20all%20offer%20four-wheelers%20with%20cute%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e12e8f2b-45de-4631-9d14-1e2f6a26f210%5C%22%3EThe%20challenges%20ahead%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20%3Ca%20href%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERobot.com%3C%2Fa%3E's%20Chavez%2C%20the%20industry's%20real%20scaling%20point%20was%20when%20the%20%26quot%3Bbig%20three%26quot%3B%20university%20food%20providers%20%E2%80%94%20Sodexo%2C%20Aramark%2C%20and%20Compass%20%E2%80%94%20got%20on%20board%20with%20delivery%20bots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrew%20Nannis%2C%20Sodexo's%20SVP%20and%20CMO%20of%20its%20campus%20segment%2C%20has%20watched%20robotic%20delivery%20grow%20since%20joining%20the%20company%20in%202019.%20He%20initially%20worried%20that%20robot%20deliveries%20would%20give%20students%20an%20excuse%20to%20hide%20in%20their%20rooms%20and%20not%20attend%20in-person%20dining.%20That%20hasn't%20panned%20out%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20students%20are%20using%20them%2C%20they're%20not%20replacing%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20Nannis%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20just%20supplementing%20and%20complementing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221843%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Avride's%20robots%20at%20OSU%20are%20pictured.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e6d46f5dbc4fd10daa7c58%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221084%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAvride's%20fleet%20of%20delivery%20robots%20at%20Ohio%20State%20University.%3Cp%3EAvride%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20still%20bumps%20in%20the%20road.%20When%20Starship%20launched%20at%20Miami%20University%20in%202023%2C%20graduate%20Meredith%20Perkins%20noticed%20that%20the%20robots%20struggled%20to%20cross%20the%20street.%20The%20issue%20never%20fully%20went%20away%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20many%20students%20I%20know%20joke%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20these%20robots%20are%20very%20slow%2C%26quot%3B%20Perkins%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFairfield's%20Perry%20once%20ordered%20coffee%20with%20her%20friend%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-customer-gets-drink-order-delivered-via-flying-drone-tiktok-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStarbucks%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20campus.%20They%20watched%20the%20robot%20stop%20moving%20on%20the%20tracking%20map%20and%20went%20out%20to%20find%20it.%20The%20robot%20was%20stuck%20on%20the%20curb.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20found%20the%20robot%2C%20helped%20it%20up%2C%20but%20it%20was%20programmed%2C%20of%20course%2C%20so%20we%20had%20to%20follow%20it%20back%20to%20my%20friend's%20apartment%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20we%20opened%20it%2C%20the%20coffee%20spilled%20all%20over%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there's%20the%20question%20of%20payment.%20The%20average%20Starship%20delivery%20fee%20is%20%242.49%20%E2%80%94%20less%20than%20a%20human%20courier's%2C%20but%20still%20a%20tough%20sum%20for%20some%20college%20students%20to%20stomach.%20Perkins%20said%20that%20Miami%20University's%20%242%20delivery%20fee%20kept%20most%20students%20from%20using%20the%20robots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESodexo's%20Nannis%20said%20that%2C%20when%20an%20additional%20charge%20was%20added%20per%20robotic%20delivery%2C%20usage%20fell%20drastically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20subscription%20model%20is%20the%20one%20that%20works%2C%26quot%3B%20Nannis%20said.%20%26quot%3BMaking%20them%20part%20of%20the%20meal%20plans%20that%20we're%20selling%2C%20I%20think%20that's%20the%20most%20important%20piece%20of%20how%20we're%20making%20this%20work%20financially.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ed499b4c-2885-473c-986d-36f526220e6d%5C%22%3EWho's%20actually%20using%20the%20robots%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20delivery%20robots%20are%20expanding%20to%20more%20and%20more%20campuses%2C%20they're%20still%20niche.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20UNC%20Charlotte%2C%20the%20robots%20opened%20up%20a%20whole%20new%209%20p.m.%20to%202%20a.m.%20dining%20period%2C%20said%20Ben%20Kolnos%2C%20Chartwells%20Higher%20Education's%20senior%20retail%20director.%20Kolnos%20estimated%20that%20late-night%20orders%20made%20up%2015%20to%2020%25%20of%20UNC%20Charlotte's%2040%2C000%20deliveries%20a%20semester.%20That's%20not%20a%20high%20volume%20for%20a%20campus%20with%2024%2C868%20undergraduate%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStudents%20mainly%20use%20them%20when%20they're%20sick%2C%20hungover%2C%20or%20holed%20up%20in%20the%20library%20studying.%20They're%20not%20coming%20close%20to%20replacing%20the%20dining%20hall%20experience.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20200%20deliveries%20a%20day%20at%20UNC%20Charlotte%2C%20the%20college%20campus%20may%20serve%20as%20a%20model%20for%20other%20companies%20looking%20to%20expand%20nationwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20used%20to%20think%20of%20this%20technology%20five%20years%20ago%20as%20futuristic%2C%20or%20that%20companies%20were%20piloting%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20Starship's%20Heinla%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20testing%20anything%20anymore.%20We're%20not%20piloting%20anything%20anymore.%20We%20know%20that%20it%20works.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-food-delivery-robots-are-conquering-college-campuses-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1760176141000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e7c9b21c1f80efbec541c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-food-delivery-robots-are-conquering-college-campuses-2025-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22College%20delivery%20robots%20were%20once%20known%20for%20being%20kicked%20and%20p