20of%20the%20city%20by%20train.%20Reading%20a%20novel%20in%20the%20train's%20quiet%20carriage%2C%20I%20was%20already%20starting%20to%20drift%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20all%20changed%20as%20I%20stepped%20off%20the%20warm%20train%20onto%20the%20breezy%20platform%2C%20then%20into%20the%20terminal%20with%20its%20clinical%20lights%20and%20squeaky%20white%20decor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20felt%20rather%20eerie%20as%20I%20wandered%20past%20some%20empty%20check-in%20desks%2C%20but%20I%20still%20felt%20confident%20that%20I%20could%20get%20some%20decent%20shuteye.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUp%20some%20escalators%2C%20I%20found%20the%20departures%20area%20where%20a%20couple%20of%20dozen%20fellow%20travelers%20were%20already%20set%20up%20for%20the%20night.%20Some%20were%20lying%20across%20rows%20of%20seats%2C%20others%20on%20the%20floor%20using%20heavy%20backpacks%20as%20pillows%2C%20and%20a%20lucky%20few%20in%20the%20cozy%20booths%20and%20armchairs%20of%20a%2024-hour%20caf%C3%A9.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20I%20was%20reassured%20by%20the%20safety%20in%20numbers%20in%20case%20of%20any%20would-be%20thieves%20during%20the%20night.%20Yet%20being%20surrounded%20by%20strangers%20still%20made%20it%20challenging%20for%20me%20to%20let%20my%20guard%20down%20and%20relax.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20folded%20a%20hoodie%20for%20a%20makeshift%20pillow%2C%20zipped%20up%20my%20jacket%20with%20my%20valuables%20inside%2C%20and%20curled%20up%20on%20the%20bench%20with%20my%20rucksack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-you-should-pack-carry-on-luggage-from-flight-attendant-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecarry-on%20size%20restrictions%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20a%20budget%20airline%20limited%20what%20I%20could%20bring%2C%20and%20another%20hoodie%20or%20a%20neck%20pillow%20could've%20made%20me%20more%20comfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20empty%20check-in%20zone%20at%20London%20Gatwick%20Airport%20at%20night%20early%20on%20Tuesday%2025%20September%2C%202025%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e8c49c5dbc4fd10daa9803%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20empty%20check-in%20zone%20as%20seen%20from%20the%20departures%20area.%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20apartment%20move%20also%20meant%20I%20had%20waylaid%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-sleep-masks%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esleep%20masks%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20picked%20up%20on%20other%20travels.%20Resorting%20to%20cupping%20my%20hand%20over%20my%20face%2C%20I%20was%20envious%20of%20the%20man%20I%20saw%20with%20a%20beanie%20pulled%20down%20over%20his%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20put%20in%20my%20headphones%20and%20tried%20to%20zone%20out%2C%20but%20struggled%20to%20feel%20sleepy.%20Around%201%20a.m.%2C%20I%20heard%20the%20sound%20of%20radios%20passing%20by%20and%20opened%20my%20eyes%20to%20see%20police%20officers%20doing%20the%20rounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20whirring%20escalators%20and%20sporadic%20low%20chatter%20were%20further%20reminders%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20I%20was%20in%20an%20airport%20terminal%20rather%20than%20tucked%20up%20in%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20another%2030%20minutes%2C%20utter%20doubt%20settled%20in.%20I%20wrote%20in%20my%20notes%20app%3A%20%26quot%3BHow%20na%C3%AFve%20I%20was%20to%20think%20'How%20bad%20could%20it%20be%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20found%20more%20comfort%20after%20changing%20position%20to%20lie%20on%20my%20back.%20I%20also%20remembered%20the%20cap%20in%20my%20bag%20and%20pulled%20it%20over%20my%20face%2C%20Indiana%20Jones-style.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20finally%20started%20to%20nod%20off.%20Then%20I%20felt%20the%20seats%20shake.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20happened%20a%20few%20times%20before%20I%20opened%20my%20eyes%20to%20see%20a%20man%20sitting%20at%20the%20end%20of%20my%20row%2C%20charging%20his%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20reminded%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BMoby-Dick%26quot%3B%20scene%20where%20Ishmael%20ends%20up%20sharing%20a%20bed%20with%20the%20cannibal%20Queequeg.%20My%20companion%20seemed%20like%20a%20perfectly%20normal%20chap%2C%20but%20that%20was%20the%20unsettling%20sense%20of%20trying%20to%20sleep%20with%20strangers%20all%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoments%20later%2C%20around%202%3A30%20a.m.%2C%20a%20trio%20of%20men%20sat%20amid%20the%20napping%20travelers%20and%20started%20holding%20court%2C%20chatting%20and%20chortling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20my%20AirPods%20then%20ran%20out%20of%20battery.%20I%20decided%20to%20go%20for%20a%20walk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECharging%20my%20phone%20at%20the%20Pret%20a%20Manger%20downstairs%2C%20I%20passed%20the%20time%20people-watching.%20Ground%20workers%20in%20hi-vis%20vests%20arriving%20for%20work%20queued%20for%20coffee.%20Two%20women%20greeted%20a%20bleary-eyed%20father%20pushing%20a%20stroller%2C%20having%20just%20arrived%20on%20a%20flight%20from%20Cyprus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20got%20me%20thinking%20how%20much%20easier%20it%20might%20be%20to%20sleep%20in%20the%20airport%20with%20the%20comfort%20of%20friends%20or%20family%20by%20your%20side.%20Or%20if%20you're%20on%20vacation%2C%20without%20the%20inherent%20stress%20of%20a%20work%20trip.%20I%20imagined%20being%20with%20my%20mates%2C%20somewhere%20hot%2C%20slightly%20hungover%2C%20waiting%20for%20a%20flight%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20some%20early%20morning%20hunger%20pangs%20and%20headed%20back%20upstairs%20to%20the%20departures%20area%2C%20hoping%20one%20of%20the%20caf%C3%A9's%20comfy%20armchairs%20might%20now%20be%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlissfully%2C%20there%20was%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ate%20a%20bacon%20roll%20before%20slouching%20down%20and%20making%20the%20most%20of%20the%20wide%20armchair.%20With%20my%20cap%20over%20my%20face%20once%20more%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fairpod-not-