Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20gold%20rally%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20stories%20in%20markets%20this%20year.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20precious%20metal%20surged%20past%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgolds-prices-rally-all-time-high-4000-etf-trading-volumes-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%244%2C000%20per%20ounce%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20first%20time%20this%20week%2C%20but%20with%20the%20latest%20records%2C%20it's%20natural%20to%20wonder%20how%20much%20you%20should%20be%20holding%20in%20your%20portfolio.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGold's%20reputation%20as%20an%20inflation%20hedge%20and%20a%20hedge%20against%20wider%20macro%20and%20geopolitical%20risks%20has%20made%20it%20attractive%20to%20investors%20this%20year.%20In%20an%20unusual%20twist%2C%20the%20price%20of%20the%20metal%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgold-price-stock-rally-unusual-explained-inflation-unrest-ai-debt-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erisen%20alongside%3C%2Fa%3E%20stocks%2C%20which%20are%20also%20near%20record%20highs.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FVQtP0%2F4%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22442%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20hedge%20fund%20legeng%20Ray%20Dalio%20said%20that%20investors%20should%20allocate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fray-dalio-gold-bitcoin-allocation-investing-us-debt-crisis-deficit-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eroughly%2015%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20their%20portfolios%20for%20either%20gold%20or%20bitcoin.%20Investing%20professionals%20speaking%20with%20Business%20Insider%20said%20that's%20probably%20a%20sensible%20allocation.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20think%20investors%20should%20hold%20at%20least%2015%25%20of%20their%20portfolio%20in%20gold%20as%20a%20replacement%20for%20other%20fixed%20income%20assets%2C%26quot%3B%20David%20Miller%2C%20CIO%20of%20Catalyst%20Funds%20and%20the%20portfolio%20manager%20of%20Strategy%20Shares%20Gold%20Enhanced%20Yield%20ETF%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BGlobal%20demand%20remains%20strong%2C%20supply%20growth%20is%20constrained%2C%20and%20real%20yields%20remain%20historically%20low%2C%20all%20of%20which%20support%20higher%20gold%20prices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWill%20Rhind%2C%20CEO%20of%20GraniteShares%2C%20a%20fund%20with%20%2411%20billion%20in%20assets%20under%20management%2C%20isn't%20quite%20as%20bullish%2C%20but%20he%20thinks%20a%20sizable%20allocation%20to%20gold%20is%20a%20good%20bet%2C%20even%20with%20prices%20at%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20a%20diversified%20portfolio%2C%20we%20typically%20see%20clients%20with%20allocations%20of%20somewhere%20between%207%25-10%25%20in%20gold.%20That%20number%20will%2C%20of%20course%2C%20vary%20significantly%20depending%20on%20factors%20such%20as%20the%20client's%20investment%20goals%2C%20risk%20tolerance%2C%20and%20general%20economic%20outlook%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20Rhind's%20perspective%2C%20a%20key%20to%20deriving%20value%20from%20gold%20investments%20is%20holding%20enough%20for%20it%20to%20be%20a%20relevant%20position%20in%20the%20portfolio%2C%20and%20a%201%25%20allocation%20won't%20be%20enough%20to%20impact%20a%20portfolio's%20performance%20in%20a%20meaningful%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20experts%20believe%20slightly%20less%20than%20the%207%25%20threshold%20makes%20the%20most%20sense.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20that%20a%205%25%20allocation%20to%20gold%20is%20a%20valuable%20addition%20to%20a%20classic%20long-term%20portfolio%20of%20stocks%20and%20bonds%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Alexander%20Lis%2C%20the%20chief%20investment%20officer%20of%20Social%20Discovery%20Ventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20risk%20of%20holding%20too%20much%20gold%20is%20that%20the%20conditions%20it's%20expected%20to%20hedge%20against%20never%20materialize%2C%20and%20that%20investors%20now%20may%20be%20too%20pessimistic%20about%20the%20wider%20debasement%20trade%20that's%20gripped%20the%20market.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGold%20tends%20to%20reflect%20expectations%20of%20currency%20debasement%20rather%20than%20actual%20debasement%20itself%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20argued.%20%26quot%3BGiven%20the%20rally%20this%20year%2C%20meeting%20current%20consensus%20expectations%20of%20further%20debasement%20would%20require%20stimulus%20even%20exceeding%20COVID%20levels.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgold-prices-investing-how-much-to-own-portfolio-allocation-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1760174102000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e94bdd1c1f80efbec561c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgold-prices-investing-how-much-to-own-portfolio-allocation-2025-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gold%20is%20surging%20to%20records%20this%20year.%20With%20prices%20above%20%244%2C000%20an%20ounce%2C%20how%20much%20should%20you%20have%20in%20your%20portfolio%3F%20We%20asked%20the%20pros%20to%20weigh%20in.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sobrient%40insider.com%20(Samuel%20O'Brient)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A33%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgold-prices-investing-how-much-to-own-portfolio-allocation-2025-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Anwar%20Ali%20opens%20up%20on%20'Bidoo'%20Amitabh's%20early%20struggle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1760174037000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-124474036%2Cimgsize-27210.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fexclusive-amitabh-bach